Package: ContextLinkr
Title: Link Individual-Level Records to Geographic Contextual Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Todd", "Burus", email = "tburus@uky.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools for geocoding location data, identifying Census
    tract geography, linking individual-level records to geographic identifiers,
    and adding contextual variables from Cancer InFocus data for multilevel
    health research. The package supports end-to-end record linkage workflows,
    retrieval of Cancer InFocus contextual measures, and lower-level helpers for
    joining user-supplied contextual data.
